text.section:
The amount of the surety bond shall be:
For a licensee who is licensed to deal only in trailers or semitrailers 15 feet or less in length, or only in boat trailers of any size $5,000;
For a licensee who is licensed to deal in the sale of new motor vehicles, an amount based on the number of new motor vehicle sales during the preceding license year, according to the following schedule:
1 to 500 vehicles $50,000;
501 to 1,000 vehicles $75,000;
1,001 to 2,500 vehicles $100,000; and
Over 2,500 vehicles $300,000; and
For a licensee who is licensed to deal only in the sale of used motor vehicles, including wholesalers, or a licensee who is licensed to deal in the sale of trailers or semitrailers over 15 feet in length, an amount based on the number of used vehicle sales, or sales of trailers or semitrailers over 15 feet in length, during the preceding license year, according to the following schedule:
1 to 250 vehicles$15,000;
251 to 500 vehicles$25,000;
501 to 1,000 vehicles$35,000;
1,001 to 2,500 vehicles$50,000; and
Over 2,500 vehicles$150,000.
